This is the root folder for the PhoneGap spike.


Some docs here:
http://wiki.phonegap.com/Roadmap
http://wiki.phonegap.com/Getting-started-with-Android-PhoneGap-in-Eclipse (lots of mistakes refer to the readme.md in src)

To create the android project do something like this.
c:\dev\phonegap-android>ruby droidgap c:\\dev\\android-sdk-windows PhoneGapSpike com.rapidftr.spike.phonegap c:\\dev\\workspace\\RapidFTR---PhoneGap-Edition\\src rapid-phonegap

